3 NEW SECTION. SECTION 4 .. CONSENT TO COLLECT AND SHARE INFORMATION REQUIRED. (1) MEDICAL
4 PREGNANCY CENTERS AND PREGNANCY CENTERS MAY NOT COLLECT ANY CONSUMER HEALTH DATA EXCEPT:
