10 (A) WITH CONSENT FROM THE CONSUMER FOR SHARING THAT IS SEPARATE AND DISTINCT FROM THE
11 CONSENT OBTAINED TO COLLECT CONSUMER HEALTH DATA; OR
12 (B) TO THE EXTENT NECESSARY TO PROVIDE A PRODUCT OR SERVICE THAT THE CONSUMER TO WHOM THE
13 DATA RELATES HAS REQUESTED.
