18 SPECIFIC WAYS IN WHICH IT WILL BE USED;
19 (C) THE CATEGORIES OF ENTITIES WITH WHOM THE CONSUMER HEALTH DATA IS SHARED; AND
20 (D) HOW THE CONSUMER CAN WITHDRAW CONSENT FROM FUTURE COLLECTION OR SHARING OF THE
21 CONSUMER'S HEALTH DATA.
